# Calgary Cohort Dataset

This repository contains Calgary cohort dataset used in the following study:

Turesky TK, Escalante ES, Loh M, Gaab N.  
*Longitudinal trajectories of brain development from infancy to school age and their relationship to literacy development*  
https://doi.org/10.1101/2024.06.29.601366

For corresponding code, please see:  
https://github.com/TeddyTuresky/Longitudinal-Trajectories-Early-Brain-Development-Language/tree/main

For the dataset information please see:  
https://osf.io/axz5r/

---

- No QC information
- **126 subjects, 431 scans in total**

---

# Data Dictionary for Measures

| Variable | Description |
|---|---|
| `PreschoolID` | Participant ID |
| `ScanID` | Scan ID |
| `Age (Years)` | Age in years |
| `Biological Sex (Female = 0; Male = 1)` | Biological sex |
| `Handedness` | Handedness |
| `Maternal Postsecondary Years of Education` | Maternal postsecondary years of education |
| `Phonological Processing Standard Score` | Phonological processing subtest of the NEPSY-II, which measures phonemic awareness |
| `Phonological Processing Raw Score` | Raw phonological processing score |
| `Speeded Naming Standard Score` | Standardized speeded naming score |
| `Speeded Naming Completion Time` | Completion time for speeded naming |
| `Speeded Naming Number Correct` | Number correct for speeded naming |

